        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks TCE for telling him of his crossed pigs. When they are grown, he would like to know whether they resemble each other.</p> 
<p>Doubts the half-bred <hi rend="italic">Gallus sonnerati</hi> will be productive, though he was assured many years ago that such a fertile half-breed once occurred.</p> 
        </abstract>
